    "Description": "You don't need all the details, but Headhunters have an interest in what happens over at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and I just got word they're being harassed by some aggressive upstarts. \n\nThe dumb sods are trying to cripple the place by taking out their <EM>~mission(Objects)</EM4>. I'm not having it.   \n\nGet there and provide some protection before everything gets destroyed. These chumps are lightweights so shouldn't be too much of a problem for you to handle. \n\nClear \u2018em all out I\u2019ll throw <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) Council Scrip</EM4> to whoever accepted this gig as a bonus.\n\n- Stows",
